  "body": "### Description of the Issue\r\n\r\nA user reported that after updating a Ledger Blue to the latest firmware (2.1) the error \"Unknown error when sending transaction. Ethkey (InvalidSignature)\" appears when trying to send a transaction. I'm not sure if this is an issue with MyCrypto or with the new firmware. The user reports that he's unable to sign transactions on other sites as well.\r\n\r\n### Steps to Reproduce\r\n\r\n1. Unlock your account with a Ledger Blue on the latest firmware\r\n2. Try to send a transaction\r\n\r\n### Description of Your Machine\r\n\r\nGoogle Chrome",
